"Filthy_Rich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"315";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Regulus";s:4:"text";s:38:"I think I&#039;m gonna leave this one.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1381889701";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cab57e";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13818897012";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#595959";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:95627;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"95627";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Regulus";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"49";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:4:"text";s:91:"I understand, and of course we can always make time for &quot;normal&quot; encounters later";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1381889763";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3eb820";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13818897693";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#7eee5b";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97115;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97115";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"151";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"315";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:4:"text";s:6:"Hello!";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382055931";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cab57e";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820559354";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#595959";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97117;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97117";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:4:"text";s:5:"Hello";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382055984";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820559902";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97121;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97121";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"151";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"315";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:4:"text";s:194:"May I ask a question? I talked to Regulus about it and he said I needed to talk to all the guides. But I&#039;m having some... Trouble getting in touch with them. You&#039;re one of them, right?";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382056068";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cab57e";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820560721";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#595959";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97123;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97123";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:4:"text";s:34:"I am, yes. What can I do for you? ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382056149";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820561543";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97124;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97124";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"151";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"315";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:4:"text";s:241:"Back on Filly, I had something with two characters of mine worked out with the mod staff. Sovereign and Adagia, more or less, were son and daughter of a small-time member of House Blueblood. I was wondering if that was alright here as well. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382056400";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cab57e";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820564043";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#595959";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97125;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97125";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:4:"text";s:52:"May I ask a couple questions about it really quick? ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382056598";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820566038";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97127;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97127";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"151";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"315";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:4:"text";s:19:"Knock yourself out!";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382056770";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cab57e";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820567743";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#595959";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97128;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97128";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:4:"text";s:60:"Is there any IC benefit to them being related to Blueblood? ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382056817";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820568227";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97129;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97129";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"151";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"315";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:4:"text";s:215:"It gives them an excuse to be in Canterlot now and then, but that&#039;s more of a meta benefit, along with the possible future story arcs of the family trying to force them into the politics and such of the houses.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382056910";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cab57e";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820569139";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#595959";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97130;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97130";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"151";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"315";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:4:"text";s:97:"Sovereign might like the influence as something that gives him power, but Adagia would care less.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382056935";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cab57e";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820569392";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#595959";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97133;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97133";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:4:"text";s:83:"So it&#039;s really more of a politcal thing? No special magic powers or anything? ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382056998";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820570041";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97135;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97135";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"151";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"315";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:4:"text";s:400:"Then again, as only teenagers cusping on the edge of adulthood, how much influence they&#039;d have is questionable anyway. And no, the two are above average talented at magic, but nothing like, super Blueblood powers or anything. Adagia is more powerful than Sovereign, but balances it out by being unlikely to use that power unless stressed in any offensive manner, and by being particularly frail.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382057086";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cab57e";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820570898";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#595959";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97136;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97136";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"151";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"315";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:4:"text";s:89:"Using Fillydelphia&#039;s stat system, they&#039;d both have high magic, but little else.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382057137";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cab57e";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820571414";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#595959";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97137;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97137";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"151";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"315";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:4:"text";s:98:"(Sovereign&#039;s magic stat being smartness, and Adagia&#039;s being Caring, if you care to know)";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382057158";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cab57e";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820571619";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#595959";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97139;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97139";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:4:"text";s:105:"And they won&#039;t be like, ruling nations or anything, just nobility like Regulus or OrionShadow, yes? ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382057184";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820571900";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97141;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97141";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"151";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"315";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:4:"text";s:199:"Well, yes! I assumed House Blueblood was a rather major house, but honestly that would probably just translate to a crapload of political intrigue and bureacracy rather than outright ruling anything.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382057249";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cab57e";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820572535";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#595959";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97144;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97144";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:4:"text";s:436:"Yeah, that&#039;s key. Personally, I wouldn&#039;t have a problem with that if it was handled the right way. As far as just having a ton of political influence and such, that&#039;s fine with me. So...yeah, I suppose it&#039;s fine with me if your characters are related to him. You will need to talk to at least one other mod, either Variety or Paige. Var is your best bet, and I&#039;ll be happy to bring it to her attention for you. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382057442";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820574472";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97147;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97147";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"151";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"315";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:4:"text";s:69:"Oh, I&#039;ve talked to Vares, she&#039;s... Been pretty busy lately.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382057510";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#cab57e";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820575146";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#595959";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97150;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97150";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:13:"SapphireNight";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"15";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:4:"text";s:27:"Did she give you an answer?";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1382057615";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#73f0f1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13820576212";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f792f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:97152;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"97152";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"151";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Filthy_Rich";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"3